### 📚 Referensi

- **Gee, J.P.** (2003). *What Video Games Have to Teach Us About Learning and Literacy.* — Buku yang memulai revolusi game based learning di dunia akademik.
- **Gentile, D.A.** (2011). "Pathological Video Game Use Among Youth." *Pediatrics.* — Studi tentang kecanduan game pada anak dan faktor-faktornya.
- **Wing, J.M.** (2006). "Computational Thinking." *Communications of the ACM.* — Mengapa berpikir komputasional penting untuk SEMUA bidang.
- **Papastergiou, M.** (2009). "Digital Game-Based Learning in High School Computer Science Education." *Computers & Education.* — Bukti efektivitas GBL untuk coding.
- **Dickey, M.** (2011). "Game Design and Learning." *Journal of Educational Computing Research.* — Tentang motivasi intrinsik dalam GBL.
- **Resnick, M.** (2017). *Lifelong Kindergarten.* MIT Press. — Tentang pembelajaran kreatif dari pengembang Scratch.
- **DragonBox Algebra** — University of Washington study (2013) tentang efektivitas game aljabar.
- **Code.org** — Data partisipasi 30% siswa AS (code.org/statistics)
- **Kapp, K.** (2012). *The Gamification of Learning and Instruction.* 

